00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:35.680
&gt;&gt;Ian Ni-Lewis: Absolutely.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.680
&gt;&gt;Reto Meier: Which is totally legitimate.

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:42.060
&gt;&gt;Ian Ni-Lewis: So this is kind of an interesting,
